HEALTHCARE COMPLIANCE NOTICE:

This software is designed for healthcare applications and may process Protected 
Health Information (PHI). Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with 
applicable healthcare regulations including but not limited to:

- Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA)
- Saudi Arabia National Platform for Health Information Exchange (NPHIES)
- General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)
- Local healthcare data protection laws

The software includes security features and audit logging capabilities, but 
proper configuration and operational procedures are the responsibility of the 
implementing organization.
